            .title-1 Hi there!
            .body-1 I'm Tyler. I am a third generation chiropractic student planning to join and continue my family's practice. In my free time, I work to develop a web-based health record system for chiropractors. I am an avid space flight enthusiast and something of a coffee aficionado.
            .body-1 Oh, and I do magic tricks.
